<TITLE> Real Madrid confirm North America friendlies </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 MADRID, June 3 (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - Real Madrid will play pre-season friendlies against Toronto FC and DC United as part of a tour to Canada and the United States in August, the Primera Liga club said on their website (www.realmadrid.com). The nine-times European champions will play at BMO Field in Toronto on Aug. 7 and two days later will take on DC United at Fedex Field in the U.S. capital. Real last made a promotional tour of North America in 2006
